335
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:42,220
[SPEAKER_02] Tako je.

336
00:29:42,220 --> 00:29:45,740
[SPEAKER_00] Znači zapravo smo izgubili svoju glavu.

337
00:29:45,740 --> 00:29:46,700
